menu "espAGC canonical yaAGC socket"

config AGC_YAAGC_NODE_PORT
    int "TCP port for yaAGC node listener"
    range 1024 65535
    default 19850
    help
        Port to bind on 0.0.0.0 for the canonical 4-byte yaAGC protocol.
        windows_yaagc_test.py picks per-pid ports above 19850 against
        upstream yaAGC.exe; using 19850 here keeps test scripts identical
        between the two builds. Under QEMU forward with
        -nic user,hostfwd=tcp::19850-:19850.

endmenu
